  "body_html": "<div class=\"header\">\n            <div class=\"hamburger\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"6\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"6\"/><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"12\"/><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"18\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"18\"/></svg></div>\n            <div class=\"h-title\">Untitled chat</div>\n            <div class=\"ellipsis\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><circle cx=\"5\" cy=\"12\" r=\"1.5\" fill=\"currentColor\"/><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"1.5\" fill=\"currentColor\"/><circle cx=\"19\" cy=\"12\" r=\"1.5\" fill=\"currentColor\"/></svg></div>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"model-chip\">\n            <span class=\"mark\"><svg><use href=\"#claude-mark\"/></svg></span>\n            Claude Opus 4.5\n            <span class=\"chev\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"/></svg></span>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"conv\">\n            <div class=\"user-msg\">Explain Bayesian inference like I'm a curious 15-year-old.</div>\n\n            <div class=\"ast-msg\">\n              <div class=\"ast-header\">\n                <span class=\"mark avatar\"><svg><use href=\"#claude-mark\"/></svg></span>\n                <span class=\"ast-sender\">Claude</span>\n                <span class=\"ast-model\">· Opus 4.5</span>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"ast-body\">\n                Imagine you're guessing what's in a friend's pocket. You start with a hunch — maybe <em>they have keys</em> — and then they hint, <em>\"it jingles when I walk\"</em>. That hint <strong>updates</strong> your belief. Bayesian inference is the math of doing that update systematically.<span class=\"cursor\"></span>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"chat-input\">\n            <div class=\"ci-attach\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"/><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"8\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"16\"/><line x1=\"8\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"16\" y2=\"12\"/></svg></div>\n            <div class=\"ci-input\">Reply to Claude…</div>\n            <div class=\"ci-send\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"19\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"5\"/><polyline points=\"5 12 12 5 19 12\"/></svg></div>\n          </div>",
